### Test API Kalkulatora Emerytalnego
### Użyj VS Code REST Client extension lub skopiuj do Postman/Insomnia

### 1. Podstawowy test - minimalny request
POST http://localhost:3000/api/calculate-pension
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "age": 30,
  "gender": "male",
  "grossSalary": 7500,
  "plannedRetirementYear": 2060
}

###

### 2. Pełny request - wszystkie parametry
POST http://localhost:3000/api/calculate-pension
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "age": 30,
  "gender": "male",
  "grossSalary": 7500,
  "workStartYear": 2015,
  "plannedRetirementYear": 2060,
  "zusAccountBalance": 50000,
  "zusSubaccountBalance": 12000,
  "includeSickLeave": true,
  "scenarioId": "moderate"
}

